text: Ella Rumpf (born 4 February 1995) is a French-born Swiss actress. She is best known for her role as Alexia in the 2016 horror drama movie Raw, Tiger in Tiger Girl (2017) and Hanna in The Divine Order (2017). ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss movie actors Category:Swiss television actors Category:Actors from Paris Category:Actors from ZÃ¼rich Category:French movie actors Category:French television actors
